| SKILL_local_render.md | Mandatory local OpenSCAD render verification protocol before any new-shape geometry prompt — v1.1 (2026-07-16) also adds an Independent Post-Fix Verification procedure for R-111 escalations (re-render the actual merged file, don't trust cc_chat_log/PR text alone) | Claude Web only — cc does NOT read this |
| SKILL_customizer_profile.md | Customizer-first workflow for aesthetic/artistic (non-dimensional) geometry decisions | Claude Web only — cc does NOT read this |
