| SKILL_reference_point_first.md | Local-datum-origin habit (ask "measured FROM what" before dimensioning) — SUPERSEDED by SKILL_product_design_skeleton.md but still the live convention for VM-01/PR-01 specifically | Before designing any new module's geometry within VM-01 or PR-01 |
| SKILL_product_design_skeleton.md | Full Top-Down Skeleton Layout + Datum Reference Frame + Parent-Child design discipline — FIRST file for any NEW product line | Before any component sizing on a product line that is NOT VM-01/PR-01 (both explicitly grandfathered, never retrofitted) |
| SKILL_viewer_update.md | Viewer PROJECTS-entry update procedure (first-time wiring or version bump) | Claude Web only — cc does NOT read this — triggered by "update the viewer" / "new design released" |
